      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit ${\\cal E}$ une ellipse de foyer $F$, directrice $D$.\nSoit $M \\in {\\cal E}$ hors de l'axe focal, et $T$ le point d'intersection\nde la tangente en $M$ et de la directrice $D$.\nMontrer que $FMT$ est rectangle en $F$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\({\\cal E}\\)</span> une ellipse de foyer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F\\)</span>, directrice <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D\\)</span>. Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M \\in {\\cal E}\\)</span> hors de l’axe focal, et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(T\\)</span> le point d’intersection de la tangente en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(M\\)</span> et de la directrice <span class=\"math inline\">\\(D\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(FMT\\)</span> est rectangle en <span class=\"math inline\">\\(F\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6bc9fd79-2c84-4844-9497-5f42d09fcece",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$M : \\begin{pmatrix}X\\cr Y\\end{pmatrix}  \\Rightarrow  T:\\begin{pmatrix}a/e\\cr b^2(e-X)/d\\end{pmatrix}\n                                \\Rightarrow  \\vec{FM}\\cdot\\vec{FT} = 0$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(M : \\begin{pmatrix}X\\cr Y\\end{pmatrix}  \\Rightarrow  T:\\begin{pmatrix}a/e\\cr b^2(e-X)/d\\end{pmatrix}\n                                \\Rightarrow  \\vec{FM}\\cdot\\vec{FT} = 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
